latest news


        our latest news  and press releases
    





    10.01.2025


        benteler showcases new products and solutions at the detroit auto show
    

from january 10 to 20, benteler will present the latest products and solutions from its automotive portfolio at the detroit auto show.


more
































    09.01.2025


        energy prices and green transformation in focus: nrw minister president hendrik wüst visits benteler
    

industry, especially in the steel sector, is facing a monumental challenge: the green transformation. the management of benteler steel/tube discussed the industrial policy framework needed for this transformation with hendrik wüst.


more





























    13.12.2024


        benteler strengthens us presence with new e-mobility plant
    

the benteler group continues to expand its us business and is building a new automotive plant in the city of wyoming, michigan. production is scheduled to begin in 2026. the plant will manufacture components for electric vehicles for a well-known us automaker.


more





























    20.11.2024


        benteler opens new threading line at its us facility in shreveport
    

benteler celebrated the opening of a new threading line at its us facility in shreveport, louisiana. the usd 20 million investment enables benteler to supply customers directly with domestically produced seamless tubes for oil and gas exploration.


more





























    12.11.2024


        sustainable construction: benteler steel/tube supplies climore® tubes to the construction industry
    

benteler steel/tube and ischebeck are setting new standards in sustainable construction: seamless climore® tubes from the benteler plant in dinslaken will be used in pioneering geotechnical applications.


more
